 del Caribe en Costa Rica" width="2500" height="1406" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-12-min.jpg 2500w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-12-min-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-12-min-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-12-min-768x432.jpg 768w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-12-min-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-12-min-2048x1152.jpg 2048w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="alignnone size-full wp-image-22301 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="playas del Caribe en Costa Rica" width="2500" height="1406"  layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img></p> <p><span class="acssf62a8">Como su propio nombre indica, su arena es de color blanco y sus aguas cristalinas forman pr√°cticamente una inmensa laguna gracias al arrecife de coral que queda muy cerca. Es </span><b>ideal si viajas en familia </b><span class="acssf62a8">o quieres relajarte al m√°ximo.</span></p> <h3><span id="Puerto_Vargas"><span class="acssf62a8">Puerto Vargas</span></span></h3> <p><span class="acssf62a8">Si sigues a lo largo de Playa Blanca en una peque√±a caminata por el litoral, llegar√°s a la punta donde el arrecife queda m√°s cerca de la costa.¬†</span></p> <p><amp-img data-hero class="alignnone size-full wp-image-22303 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-13-min.jpg" alt="playas del Caribe en Costa Rica" width="2500" height="1406" srcset="https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-13-min.jpg 2500w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-13-min-510x287.jpg 510w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Playas-13-min-900x506.jpg 900w, https://asuaire.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/20